{"tid":2155224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple、FB 等 52 間科企聯署起訴特朗普　禁外籍員工入境扼殺科企創新","createTime":"2020-08-13T15:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T19:10:03.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cb101a0569d10daa871f965ed8bc6cc842597adb","tid":2155224,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Apple、FB 等 52 間科企聯署起訴特朗普　禁外籍員工入境扼殺科企創新</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據《路透社》報導，美國最大的製造業工業貿易協會 &mdash;&mdash;美國全國製造協會（the National Association of Manufacturers）在加州提起，該會代表 50 個州各個工業部門的 14000 家小型和大型製造業公司，起訴美國總統特朗普停止發放 H-1B 工作簽證以及限制外籍勞工入境的行政令，Apple、Google、Microsoft、Facebook 等科技巨頭皆有份參與簽署這次的聯名訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/13/tech-giants-denounced-trump/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1Om23s7TDst2G3kf2ayE5HaSLlmjAFXv8kMEfb8ps8yW9sW-Me_Ntfpn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F13%2Ftech-giants-denounced-trump%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Om23s7TDst2G3kf2ayE5HaSLlmjAFXv8kMEfb8ps8yW9sW-Me_Ntfpn4&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=399a4233\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/13/tech-giants-denounced-trump/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1Om23s7TDst2G3kf2ayE5HaSLlmjAFXv8kMEfb8ps8yW9sW-Me_Ntfpn4</a>"},{"pid":"3f444f7aeaa681fd541635abb7d2bf725e398791","tid":2155224,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"Trump 又做乜自爆⋯"},{"pid":"5e13c8352740c4f3f6bfc3156b1a653e4be98dbe","tid":2155224,"uid":49979,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"請多d本地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />創造職位唔好咩"},{"pid":"59b9875897332d0b6cef123e290c9a5f5b26e0ca","tid":2155224,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"想點 <br />\n封關又屌 <br />\n唔封又屌"},{"pid":"a3c022d982dbbd8985e24470264434931790685